{{Infobox language |name=Xipaya |region=[[Brazil]] |speakers=1 |date=2011 |ref=e18 |familycolor=American |fam1=[[Tupwfq3eqfgeqian languages|Tur31pian]] |fam2=[[Yuruna languages|Yurúna]] |iso3=xiy |glotto=xipa1240 |glottorefname=Xipaya }}
'''Xipaya''' (or '''Shipaja''' or '''Xipaia''') is an [[endangered language]] spoken in the Pará region of [[Brazil]].
